{"tid":845744,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"佢教朗性行為 專玩雞姦兼夾跪 今晚雞姦show俾你睇","createTime":"2018-10-03T01:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T03:06:35.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ee1f103af16eebabcf179b45e3ed78a0722240f8","tid":845744,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T01:52:45.000Z","msg":"C7狗真巴閉 剝清光豬點樣計 C7媽媽今晚做雞<br />\n佢教朗性行為 專玩雞姦兼夾跪 今晚雞姦show俾你睇<br />\n<br />\nC7狗真真巴閉 出魔爪多多姿勢 亂吹他想去掗位<br />\n賤朗或朗迷自己睇 都無問題<br />\n<br />\n小花不理他 吊打他.....<br />\n老吹win小花 所以垃圾賤朗 正一契弟<br />\n<br />\n賤種朗好閪 好閪 但係又好撚廢<br />\n圖畫美麗 顏色美麗 立體咁滯<br />\n<br />\n賤種朗好閪 好閪 但係又好撚廢<br />\n姐姐俏麗 媽媽秀麗<br />\n獨在幻想中 做臭雞"},{"pid":"bb8d958e75fba0952110401526149cbf4d79cdc0","tid":845744,"uid":58811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:03:01.000Z","msg":"騎哥咩歌黎"},{"pid":"e0c10ad1b6922d93346e4a92c351f8ed24e82b52","tid":845744,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb8d958e75fba0952110401526149cbf4d79cdc0","tid":845744,"uid":58811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:03:01.000Z","msg":"騎哥咩歌黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:03:49.000Z","msg":"龍虎豹好睇"},{"pid":"a3c59dc1ecdca846b73f731e5425160547b884e3","tid":845744,"uid":7940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T03:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/26/114228_d5941c787393ac56d6e8eadb05def154.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F26%2F114228_d5941c787393ac56d6e8eadb05def154.jpeg&h=825bc3b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}